        <head><num xml:lang="en">95</num>. <term xml:lang="ta">vicakattiṉ peyar</term></head>
      <p>
        <list xml:lang="en">
          <item>ed. Caṇmukam Piḷḷai &amp; Cuntaramūrtti 1990, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/20240820_20240820_1903/page/41/mode/1up">41</ref>;</item>
