      </list>
      </p>
        <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Tiv1.95">
          <l>muṟamē muṟṟil vaikāci yaṉilanāṭ</l>
          <l>peṟumē cuḷaku<anchor xml:id="Tiv1.95-n1"/> vicākanāṭ peyarē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
            <l>a <foreign xml:lang="ta-Latn">Muṟam</foreign> [winnow], a <foreign xml:lang="ta-Latn">Muṟṟil</foreign> [winnow], <foreign xml:lang="ta-Latn">Vaikāci</foreign>, the <foreign xml:lang="ta-Latn">Aṉilam</foreign> asterism</l>
            <l>&amp; a <foreign xml:lang="ta-Latn">Cuḷaku</foreign> [winnow] are words for the <foreign xml:lang="ta-Latn">Vicākam</foreign> asterism.</l>
        </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
